<html lang='ko' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <meta http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible' content='IE=edge' />
    <link
      rel='preconnect'
      href='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net'
      crossorigin='anonymous'
    />
    <link
      rel='stylesheet'
      href='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/static/pretendard.min.css'
    />
    <style type='text/css'>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f6f4f2;
        font-family:
          'Pretendard',
          -apple-system,
          BlinkMacSystemFont,
          'Segoe UI',
          sans-serif;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        color: #1c1917;
      }
      table {
        border-collapse: collapse;
        border-spacing: 0;
      }
      td {
        border-collapse: collapse;
        vertical-align: top;
        padding: 0;
      }
      img {
        border: 0;
        display: block;
        max-width: 100%;
      }
      a {
        color: #292524;
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body
    style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #F6F4F2; font-family: 'Pretendard', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;"
  >
    <!-- Outer wrapper -->
    <table
      border='0'
      cellpadding='0'
      cellspacing='0'
      width='100%'
      style='background-color: #F6F4F2; min-height: 100vh;'
    >
      <tr>
        <td align='center' style='padding: 48px 16px;'>

          <!-- Container card -->
          <table
            border='0'
            cellpadding='0'
            cellspacing='0'
            style='max-width: 560px; width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #E5E0DB; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden;'
          >

            <!-- Header -->
            <tr>
              <td
                style='padding: 28px 40px 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E0DB;'
              >
                <table border='0' cellpadding='0' cellspacing='0' width='100%'>
                  <tr>
                    <td valign='middle'>
                      <!-- SVG 로고 + 워드마크 -->
                      <table border='0' cellpadding='0' cellspacing='0'>
                        <tr>
                          <!-- B 심볼 아이콘 -->
                          <td valign='middle' style='padding-right: 8px;'>
                            <svg
                              width='28'
                              height='28'
                              viewBox='0 0 180 180'
                              fill='none'
                              xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
                            >
                              <rect
                                width='180'
                                height='180'
                                rx='38'
                                fill='#292524'
                              />
                              <line
                                x1='58'
                                y1='42'
                                x2='62'
                                y2='138'
                                stroke='#FAFAF9'
                                stroke-width='14'
                                stroke-linecap='round'
                              />
                              <path
                                d='M 60,42 C 60,42 118,38 120,68 C 122,88 65,90 63,90'
                                fill='none'
                                stroke='#FAFAF9'
                                stroke-width='13'
                                stroke-linecap='round'
                                stroke-linejoin='round'
                              />
                              <path
                                d='M 60,90 C 60,90 126,86 128,118 C 130,142 62,140 59,138'
                                fill='none'
                                stroke='#FAFAF9'
                                stroke-width='13'
                                stroke-linecap='round'
                                stroke-linejoin='round'
                              />
                            </svg>
                          </td>
                          <!-- 워드마크 -->
                          <td valign='middle'>
                            <div
                              style='font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: #292524; letter-spacing: -0.3px; line-height: 1;'
                            >
                              Bluecollar
                              <span style='font-weight: 700;'>CV</span>
                            </div>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      </table>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Body -->
            <tr>
              <td style='padding: 40px 40px;'>
                {{{body}}}
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Footer -->
            <tr>
              <td
                style='background-color: #F6F4F2; padding: 24px 40px; border-top: 1px solid #E5E0DB;'
              >
                <table border='0' cellpadding='0' cellspacing='0' width='100%'>
                  <tr>
                    <td style='text-align: center;'>
                      <div style='margin-bottom: 12px;'>
                        <a
                          href='https://bluecollar.cv'
                          style='font-size: 12px; color: #6B5E57; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;'
                        >서비스</a>
                        <span style='color: #E5E0DB;'>·</span>
                        <a
                          href='https://bluecollar.cv/privacy'
                          style='font-size: 12px; color: #6B5E57; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;'
                        >개인정보처리방침</a>
                        <span style='color: #E5E0DB;'>·</span>
                        <a
                          href='https://bluecollar.cv/terms'
                          style='font-size: 12px; color: #6B5E57; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;'
                        >이용약관</a>
                      </div>
                      <p
                        style='margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 11px; color: #6B5E57; line-height: 1.5;'
                      >이메일에 답장하시면 support@bluecollar.cv로 전달됩니다.</p>
                      <p
                        style='margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 11px; color: #6B5E57;'
                      >수신을 원하지 않으시면
                        <a
                          href='https://bluecollar.cv/unsubscribe?email={{recipientEmail}}'
                          style='color: #292524; text-decoration: underline;'
                        >여기</a>를 클릭하세요.</p>
                      <p
                        style='margin: 16px 0 0; font-size: 11px; color: #B8AFA9;'
                      >© 2026 BlueCollar. All rights reserved.</p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

          </table>
          <!-- /Container card -->

        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    <!-- /Outer wrapper -->
  </body>
</html>